Currently if JIRA needs to send one notification to more than one user, JIRA will create multiple items in the Mail Queue and create one session in the Mail Server per user.

This creates a huge amount of extra emails if there are many watchers on an issues or a group set in the notification scheme and can cause the Mail Queue to get overloaded by a single comment added to an issue.

It would be great if JIRA could use the same mail session and send the same email to all users to be notified.

